# 5b5d705916db45ee8c5d23f057254a95
msgid "This option will cause calibre to analyze blank lines included within the document.  If every paragraph is interleaved with a blank line, then calibre will remove all those blank paragraphs.  Sequences of multiple blank lines will be considered scene breaks and retained as a single paragraph.  This option differs from the 'Remove Paragraph Spacing' option under 'Look and Feel' in that it actually modifies the HTML content, while the other option modifies the document styles.  This option can also remove paragraphs which were inserted using calibre's 'Insert blank line' option."
